sequenceDiagram
    actor EditorA as Editor A
    actor EditorB as Editor B
    participant FE_A as Frontend A
    participant FE_B as Frontend B
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant WSMgr as WebSocket Manager
    participant Cache as Redis (Presence)
    participant DB as MongoDB

    Note over EditorA, DB: Editor A opens project
    EditorA->>FE_A: Opens project
    FE_A->>API: WS /ws/projects/{id}?token={jwt}
    API->>API: Validate JWT
    API->>WSMgr: Register connection in room {project_id}
    WSMgr->>Cache: SADD presence:{project_id} user_id_A
    WSMgr-->>FE_A: { type: user_joined, actor: A }

    Note over EditorB, DB: Editor B joins the same project
    EditorB->>FE_B: Opens project
    FE_B->>API: WS /ws/projects/{id}?token={jwt}
    API->>WSMgr: Register connection in room {project_id}
    WSMgr->>Cache: SADD presence:{project_id} user_id_B
    WSMgr-->>FE_A: { type: user_joined, actor: B }
    WSMgr-->>FE_B: { type: user_joined, actor: B }

    Note over EditorA, DB: Editor A places a camera
    EditorA->>FE_A: Drop camera on map
    FE_A->>FE_A: 300ms debounce
    FE_A->>API: POST /projects/{id}/cameras<br/>{ position, bearing, model_id, ... }
    API->>DB: Compute FOV + insert CameraInstance
    DB-->>API: Saved CameraInstance
    API->>WSMgr: broadcast camera_added (exclude FE_A)
    WSMgr-->>FE_B: { type: camera_added, payload: CameraInstance }
    API-->>FE_A: 200 OK — CameraInstance with fov_geojson
    FE_A->>FE_A: Update cameraSlice in Zustand
    FE_B->>FE_B: Merge camera_added into cameraSlice

    Note over EditorB, DB: Editor B disconnects
    FE_B-->>WSMgr: WS close
    WSMgr->>Cache: SREM presence:{project_id} user_id_B
    WSMgr-->>FE_A: { type: user_left, actor: B }
